  "title": "Electrical Engineer",
  "description": "<p>In this role, you will have the unique opportunity to engage in Software Programming, Electrical Design, develop, prototype the hardware and software of equipment.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We're looking for motivated engineers willing to work in a quality driven environment with a keen sense of product development to produce technologically superior products. One thing is for sure, you will be working closely with an experienced team, that will always make you feel that you a part of a dynamic organization.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities</p>\n<p>• Responsible for selection of electrical components.</p>\n<p>• Design and updating of electrical drawings</p>\n<p>• Responsible for software programming (PLC), testing and commissioning of machine.</p>\n<p>• Coordinate with relevant department to meet customer requirement and on time delivery.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>• Degree/Diploma in Electrical Engineering</p>\n<p>• Experience in Electrical circuit design.</p>\n<p>• Experience in PLC / C# / C++ programming.</p>\n<p>• Entry Level candidates are welcome</p>",
